---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About RDH Robotics"
  description="Learn about RDH Robotics, our mission to make advanced cyber security and IoT technology accessible, and our commitment to innovation and quality."
>
  <Container class="border-t border-neutral-200 py-14">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">About Us</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-950">
        Welcome to RDH Robotics
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-neutral-600">
        At RDH Robotics, we specialize in cutting-edge IoT devices, embedded systems, and educational pentesting tools that empower industries, innovators, and security professionals across India.
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-neutral mt-12 max-w-none prose-h2:text-3xl prose-h2:tracking-tight prose-p:leading-8 prose-li:leading-8">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          Founded by Rajbhar Divesh, RDH Robotics began as a bold startup with a clear vision:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>To deliver innovative IoT devices that enable industries to monitor, automate, and optimize operations.</li>
          <li>To develop next-generation embedded systems that add intelligence and efficiency to machines and processes.</li>
          <li>To design educational and pentesting tools that inspire learners, researchers, and security professionals to explore, experiment, and innovate.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          From a single idea to a growing company, our journey reflects creativity, problem-solving, and customer-first thinking.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We're committed to making advanced cyber security technology, IoT solutions, and development boards accessible to businesses, developers, and tech enthusiasts. Our carefully curated selection combines reliability, performance, and affordability to meet the evolving needs of modern technology.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <p>
          From robust cyber security devices and IoT monitoring systems to versatile development boards and pentesting tools, we provide the complete toolkit you need to build secure, innovative projects. Whether you're a professional enhancing your security infrastructure, a researcher exploring new possibilities, or an educator inspiring the next generation, we have the right solutions for you.
        </p>

        <h2>Get in Touch.</h2>
        <p>
          Have questions? We're here to help. Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@rdhrobotics.in">support@rdhrobotics.in</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </Container>
</Layout>
